Hello there!!!

This one was my very first map, and after playing with it at my clan's server and having a good feedback from my friends, I decided to post in here.

Basically it is a fight yard with five-seven pistols with walls made of water!!!

It is a small map, but with some fun on it.

enjoy it...


PS: the SKIN that shows in the screenshot, DOES NOT come with the package, it was just for taking the screenshot. I don't take any credit for the skin used.
